text: The University of Utah is a public, co-ed university in Salt Lake City, Utah. The University of Utah's athletic team's are called the Utes, which is named after a tribe of Native Americans called the Ute Tribe and they have 17 varsity teams. ==Other websites== Category:Colleges and universities in Utah Category:Big 12 Conference Category:Salt Lake City Category:1850 establishments in the United States
